    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely pristine, showroom-quality vehicle! This car is in mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. With a flawless exterior and a spotless interior, it\u2019s a rare find that offers a truly premium driving experience for its next lucky owner!",
